Taxa are arranged phylogenetically when possible; however, for many groups phylogenetic relationships are not known. These taxa are arranged alphabetically.

 

Like all such works this checklist is incomplete. The author may be reached at mailto:mdoverton@stx.rr.com and would appreciate learning of any additional species found in Northeast Mexico. Any additions to this checklist require determination by an expert, of a specimen or an identifiable photograph.
